:\\\"https://picture-search.skywork.ai/skills/upload/2026-04-17/21efe059834d48fdb33d24f0285fb2de_fe61b.png\\\",\\\"alt\\\":\\\"橄欖油的風土密碼：為什麼西班牙、希臘與義大利的同種橄欖，能孕育出截然不同的靈魂？ — 知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\\\",\\\"fill\\\":true,\\\"className\\\":\\\"object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300\\\",\\\"unoptimized\\\":true}]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"p-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-sm font-bold text-olive-800 line-clamp-2 group-hover:text-olive-600 transition-colors\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"橄欖油的風土密碼：為什麼西班牙、希臘與義大利的同種橄欖，能孕育出截然不同的靈魂？\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":[7,\\\" 分鐘閱讀\\\"]}]]}]]}]}]]}]]}]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"24:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-olive-100\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-xl font-bold text-olive-800 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"💬\\\"}],\\\" 常見問題\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"space-y-3\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"details\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"summary\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"橄欖油多酚含量多少才算高品質？\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"▾\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"根據 EFSA（歐洲食品安全局）的健康宣稱標準，每日攝取含 5mg 羥基酪醇（Hydroxytyrosol）的橄欖油可保護 LDL 免受氧化壓力。換算成橄欖油，理想的總酚含量（TPC）應在 250mg/kg 以上，醫療級 EVOO 通常達 400-800mg/kg。市面多數橄欖油的多酚含量僅 50-150mg/kg，差距極大。\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"details\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"summary\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"如何在購買時確認橄欖油的多酚含量？\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"▾\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"有三個實用方法：(1) 直接要求供應商提供 CoA（Certificate of Analysis）分析證明書，查看 TPC（Total Polyphenol Content）數值；(2) 尋找 NYIOOC、EVOOLEUM Guide 等國際競賽金牌得主，這些油款通常有公開的多酚檢測數據；(3) 觀察感官特徵——真正高多酚油在吞嚥後 3-5 秒應有明顯的喉嚨刺激感（Oleocanthal）和苦味（Oleuropein）。\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"details\\\",\\\"2\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"summary\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"橄欖油開封後多酚含量會下降嗎？\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"▾\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"是的，多酚含量在開封後會因氧化而持續下降。研究顯示，橄欖油多酚在採收後每 12 個月約流失 30-50%；開封後應在 2-3 個月內使用完畢，且需避光（深色瓶或錫罐）、避熱（室溫陰涼處）、避免接觸氧氣（用後立即蓋緊）。超過採收後 18 個月的橄欖油，即使未開封，多酚功效也大幅衰退。\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"details\\\",\\\"3\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"summary\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"標籤上標示「初榨」和「特級初榨」有什麼差別？\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"▾\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"根據 IOC 標準：特級初榨橄欖油（Extra Virgin Olive Oil, EVOO）要求游離酸度 ≤0.8%、過氧化值 ≤20 meq/kg，且通過感官評鑑無缺陷；初榨橄欖油（Virgin Olive Oil）酸度 ≤2%，允許輕微感官缺陷；精製橄欖油（Refined Olive Oil）經化學或物理精製，多酚幾乎為零，健康功效極低。購買時只有 EVOO 才值得為健康功效付費。\\\"}]]}]]}]]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"25:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-olive-100\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-lg font-bold text-olive-800 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"📚\\\"}],\\\" 參考文獻\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"ol\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"space-y-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-sm text-gray-500 flex gap-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-olive-400 font-medium shrink-0\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"[\\\",1,\\\"]\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"EFSA (2011). Scientific Opinion on the substantiation of health claims re